categories: Category:Enlisted stormtroopers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: Givens was a Human male who served as a stormtrooper, holding the rank of corporal, during the Galactic Civil War.

In 1 BBY, he was a member of the platoon led by Cadet Leader Kyle Katarn where they were assigned aboard the Star Destroyer Imperator to take control over AX-456. Along with Morely, he was the team's demolitions expert. He was soon killed in the battle.
